&&+\frac{1}{2}\int_{\Omega \times \{y=R\}}y^{2-2s}(\nabla w)^{T}B(x)(\nabla
w)\;dx-\int_{\Omega \times \{y=R\}}y^{1-2s}(z\cdot \nabla w)\frac{\partial w
